            <svg width="20" height="20" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 19c-5 1.5-5-2.5-7-3m14 6v-3.87a3.37 3.37 0 00-.94-2.61c3.14-.35 6.44-1.54 6.44-7A5.44 5.44 0 0020 4.77 5.07 5.07 0 0019.91 1S18.73.65 16 2.48a13.38 13.38 0 00-7 0C6.27.65 5.09 1 5.09 1A5.07 5.07 0 005 4.77a5.44 5.44 0 00-1.5 3.78c0 5.42 3.3 6.61 6.44 7A3.37 3.37 0 009 18.13V22"></path></svg>
